Developer Terms of Use
des:
Bank effortlessly, using your voice with the Westpac Banking skill.
Check your account balances, recent transactions and reward points status.

To get started, simply enable the Westpac skill and link up to three eligible accounts. Create a 4 digit passcode for an added layer of security. 

Simply say, “Alexa, open Westpac”. Once the skill is open, manage your eligible accounts using some of the following commands:

“What’s my account balance?”
“What’s my credit card balance?”
“What are my recent transactions?”
“What are my last 5 transactions?”
 “How many reward points do I have?”
 “What can I ask you?”

Find out more about the Westpac Banking skill at https://westpac.com.au/alexa.

Tell us what you think.
Share your feedback and suggestions on how we can improve our Westpac Banking Skill via our feedback form at https://westpac.com.au/alexa
https://www.westpac.com.au/personal-banking/online-banking/alexa/voice-banking-feedback/


Things you should know
 
Westpac’s Online Banking Terms and Conditions apply and are available at www.westpac.com.au. Westpac skills are only available for use by Westpac Australia customers. Internet connection is required. Normal data charges apply. For a list of eligible accounts and for further information visit westpac.com.au/alexa.
